{"tid":1653190,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載自時事台][國際線] Apple 將用戶上網紀錄送俾蚑共","createTime":"2019-10-14T03:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T03:37:13.000Z","uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd08b380c7808f18348550ab5f7cb11fea6900b","tid":1653190,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:34:44.000Z","msg":"有人發現咗而家 safari 會將你上過嘅網 send 去騰訊做&quot;安全檢查&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://serve.reclaimthenet.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/apple-safari-ip-addresses-tencent-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fserve.reclaimthenet.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Fapple-safari-ip-addresses-tencent-2.jpg&h=f4823a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講即係你safari，甚至其他app (chrome/firefox) 入面上過嘅網，騰訊都會知<br />\n<br />\n集中推呢個 twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/matthew_d_green/status/1183391221861027841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmatthew_d_green%2Fstatus%2F1183391221861027841&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=738d6443\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmatthew_d_green%2Fstatus%2F1183391221861027841&h=704bfd3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/matthew_d_green/status/1183391221861027841</a><br />\n<br />\n自救方法可以閂咗佢，但咁樣上網要小心啲，因為除咗騰訊，本身google都會幫手做安全檢查，都提過我幾次上緊釣魚網<br />\n<img src=\"https://serve.reclaimthenet.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/apple-safari-ip-addresses-tencent-3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fserve.reclaimthenet.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Fapple-safari-ip-addresses-tencent-3.jpeg&h=eccd2f62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bcbb260b33649ead08bd68fd3b4c7c610ac2411","tid":1653190,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"source:<br />\n[國際線] Apple 將用户上網紀錄送俾中共<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/165